pylapp.tapster.client.android.tools.properties

Class AssetsPropertiesReaderSkeleton

  • pylapp.tapster.client.android.tools.properties.AssetsPropertiesReaderSkeleton
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertiesReaderStub

    public class AssetsPropertiesReaderSkeleton
implements PropertiesReaderStub

    Skeleton based on design pattern Bridge which provides the definitions of methods to call so as to deal with properties. The goal here is to enable and disable features from the source code, with the "configuration as code" idea. Thus it will be easy to remove or add features for debugging, staging, production releases APK, etc.
